description: Great Price! Corner 1 bed, 1.5 bathrooms PLUS private outdoor balcony! One Valet Garage space. The expansive layout features abundant natural light, hardwood flooring, and modern finishes throughout, creating a bright and airy atmosphere. The open-concept kitchen boasts custom Italian cabinetry, Thermador integrated appliances, and a breakfast bar that overlooks the living and dining spaces.The bedroom is generously sized, providing ample closet space. The en-suite spa-like marble bathroom offers a relaxing retreat, with a separate powder room for guests.In unit washer & dryer plus storage. The private deck off the living room is the perfect break any time of the day.The unit's elegant design extends to the expansive views of the Seaport and private pool area. The Echelon is rich with amenities, include 3 pools, a state-of-the-art indoor basketball court, golf simulator, a Pilates/yoga studio, and a dog run. World class 24/7 concierge, doorman and valet services.
